collectionMetadata.name: Net Amount Withdrawn from Ordinary & Special Account for Investment, Annual
collectionMetadata.description:
Net amount withdrawn from Ordinary & Special Account for investment in calendar year.
Negative value means amount refunded to the account is more than the amount withdrawn from the account. Figures are rounded to the nearest hundred thousand dollars.
